WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
What Actually Moves Outcomes

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
Better outcomes usually come from sharper checkpoints, not bigger plans.

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Define the baseline first, then test one intervention before scaling it wider.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Run a compact loop: signal, decision, action, evidence, then adjust next cycle.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
The measurable win is fewer repeated errors and clearer accountability.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
Apply this to one active project over 10 days, then scale only after evidence is stable.
